org.gvsig.raster.georeferencing.framework

Interface GeoreferencingFrameworkManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeoreferencingAndamiFrameworkManagerImpl

    public interface GeoreferencingFrameworkManager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's business logic. It is the library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage GeoreferencingFrameworkServices.
